{{Italic title prefixed|3}}
Two ships of the [[United States Navy]] have borne the name '''''Billfish''''', after the [[billfish]]. 

* The {{USS|Billfish|SS-286}}, was a ''Balao''-class submarine, commissioned in 1943 and struck in 1968.

* The {{USS|Billfish|SSN-676}}, was a ''Sturgeon''-class submarine, commissioned in 1971 and struck in 1999.

